prompt: Image Prompt: Generate an image depicting a vast, celestial landscape with a luminous, infinite glow emanating from a central figure symbolizing the omnipresence and boundless nature of an infinite God. Include elements like stars, galaxies, and ethereal light to convey a sense of divine magnitude and eternity. The central figure should exude majesty and grace, evoking a profound sense of awe and reverence. This imagery should encapsulate the concept of an eternal, all-encompassing deity in a visually captivating and spiritually resonant manner.
